{"type":"answer","id":22341,"parentType":"question","parentId":4276,"uid":15,"contents":"不会，共产党的绞肉机称号不是白来的，幻想拿枪的能倒戈不免太幼稚了，共产党早想到了。<br>\n<br>\n同样是阅兵踢正步，苏联红军和解放军都是后一排的枪口和刺刀顶着前面人的脑袋，这个传统保持至今，哪天你看到这玩意儿变了再来问这个问题。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ck9qWW9.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ck9qWW9.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ck9qWW9.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/yAZO1oB.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yAZO1oB.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/yAZO1oB.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/3sdu3Sh.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3sdu3Sh.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/3sdu3Sh.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/eDOHp1a.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eDOHp1a.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/eDOHp1a.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n看看国军的正步，一直都是枪口朝天<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/pWFgMtQ.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pWFgMtQ.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/pWFgMtQ.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/EzO6cu8.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EzO6cu8.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/EzO6cu8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n美军没有正步，但阅兵也都是枪口不会指着自己人的脑袋<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/g698kkg.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/g698kkg.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/g698kkg.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/RExjvsF.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RExjvsF.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/RExjvsF.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n同样的军事思想指导下，这些网评员、审核员干工作之前，先会在安排背后的督导队。","date":"2019-05-21","agreeCount":27,"discussionCount":1}